{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2000,"text":"So, these are"},{"time":4000,"text":"the Dark Ages."},{"time":7000,"text":"And the Dark Ages are the time between"},{"time":9000,"text":"when you put away the Lego"},{"time":11000,"text":"for the last time as a kid,"},{"time":13000,"text":"and you decide as an adult that it is okay to play with a kid's toy."},{"time":18000,"text":"Started out with my then four-year-old:"},{"time":21000,"text":"\"Oh, should buy the kid some Lego."},{"time":23000,"text":"That stuff's cool.\""},{"time":25000,"text":"Walked into the Lego store."},{"time":27000,"text":"Bought him this."},{"time":29000,"text":"It's totally appropriate for a four-year-old."},{"time":31000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":34000,"text":"I think the box says --"},{"time":36000,"text":"let's see here --"},{"time":38000,"text":"\"8 to 12\" on it."},{"time":40000,"text":"I turn to my wife and said, \"Who are we buying this for?\""},{"time":43000,"text":"She's like, \"Oh, us.\" I'm like, \"Okay. All right. That's cool.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":46000,"text":"Pretty soon it got a little bit out of control."},{"time":49000,"text":"The dining room looked like this."},{"time":52000,"text":"You walk there, and it hurts."},{"time":56000,"text":"So we took a room downstairs in the basement"},{"time":59000,"text":"that had been used as sort of an Abu Ghraib annex."},{"time":62000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":67000,"text":"Torture, very funny."},{"time":69000,"text":"Wow, you guys are great."},{"time":71000,"text":"And we put down those little floor tiles,"},{"time":74000,"text":"and then I went onto eBay"},{"time":76000,"text":"and bought 150 pounds of Lego --"},{"time":79000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":81000,"text":"which is insane."},{"time":83000,"text":"My daughter -- the day we got it, I was tucking her in --"},{"time":86000,"text":"and I said,"},{"time":88000,"text":"\"Honey, you're my treasure.\""},{"time":90000,"text":"And she said, \"No, the Lego is the treasure.\""},{"time":93000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":95000,"text":"And then she said, \"Dad, we're Lego rich.\""},{"time":98000,"text":"I was like, \"Yeah."},{"time":100000,"text":"I suppose we are.\""},{"time":103000,"text":"So then once you do that"},{"time":105000,"text":"you're like, \"Oh, crap. Where am I going to put all this?\""},{"time":107000,"text":"So you go to The Container Store"},{"time":109000,"text":"and spend an enormous amount of money,"},{"time":111000,"text":"and then you start this crazy sorting process"},{"time":114000,"text":"that never --"},{"time":116000,"text":"it's just nuts."},{"time":118000,"text":"Whatever."}]},{"cues":[{"time":120000,"text":"So then you realize there are these conventions."},{"time":122000,"text":"And you go to one of these conventions, and some dude built the Titanic."},{"time":124000,"text":"And you're like, \"Holy shit!"},{"time":126000,"text":"He had to come in like a truck,"},{"time":128000,"text":"a semi, with this thing.\""},{"time":130000,"text":"And then someone built this -- this is the Smith Tower in Seattle."},{"time":132000,"text":"Just beautiful."},{"time":134000,"text":"And there's a dude selling these"},{"time":136000,"text":"aftermarket weapons for Lego,"},{"time":139000,"text":"because Lego -- the Danish --"},{"time":141000,"text":"no, they're not into guns."},{"time":143000,"text":"But the Americans? Oh, we'll make some guns for Lego, no problem."},{"time":147000,"text":"And at a certain point, you look around,"},{"time":149000,"text":"you're like, \"Whoa, this is a really nerdy crowd.\""},{"time":153000,"text":"And I mean like this is a nerdy crowd,"},{"time":155000,"text":"but that's like a couple of levels above furries."},{"time":157000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":159000,"text":"The nerds here, they get laid --"},{"time":162000,"text":"except for the lady with the condoms in her pocket --"},{"time":164000,"text":"and you say to yourself at some point,"},{"time":166000,"text":"\"Am I part of this group? Like, am I into this?\""},{"time":169000,"text":"And I was just like, \"Yeah, I guess I am."},{"time":171000,"text":"I'm coming out."},{"time":173000,"text":"I'm kind of into this stuff, and I'm going to stop being embarrassed.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":175000,"text":"So then you really get into it,"},{"time":177000,"text":"and you're like, \"Well, the Lego people in Denmark, they've got all this software"},{"time":179000,"text":"to let you build your own virtually.\""},{"time":182000,"text":"And so this is like this CAD program where you build it."},{"time":185000,"text":"And then whatever you design virtually,"},{"time":187000,"text":"you click the button and it shows up at your doorstep a week later."},{"time":190000,"text":"And then some of the designs that people do"},{"time":192000,"text":"they actually sell in the store."},{"time":194000,"text":"The Lego guys don't give you any royalties, strangely,"},{"time":197000,"text":"but some user made this and then it sold."},{"time":200000,"text":"And it's pretty amazing actually."}]},{"cues":[{"time":202000,"text":"Then you notice that if that"},{"time":204000,"text":"Lego-provided CAD program isn't enough,"},{"time":206000,"text":"there's an entire open-source, third-party,"},{"time":208000,"text":"independent Lego CAD program"},{"time":211000,"text":"that lets you do 3D modeling"},{"time":213000,"text":"and 3D rendering"},{"time":215000,"text":"and make, in fact, movies out of Lego,"},{"time":218000,"text":"3D films"},{"time":220000,"text":"of which there are thousands on YouTube,"},{"time":222000,"text":"and some of them sort of mimicking famous films"},{"time":224000,"text":"and some totally original content --"},{"time":226000,"text":"just beautiful --"},{"time":228000,"text":"and people recreating all sorts of things."},{"time":230000,"text":"I have to take a moment."},{"time":232000,"text":"I love the guy who's like running away"},{"time":234000,"text":"with his clasps, his hooks."},{"time":236000,"text":"Okay. Anyway."}]},{"cues":[{"time":238000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":241000,"text":"There's a whole programming language and robotics tool,"},{"time":243000,"text":"so if you want to teach someone how to program,"},{"time":245000,"text":"kid, adult, whatever it is."},{"time":247000,"text":"And the guy that made this,"},{"time":249000,"text":"he made a slot machine out of Lego."},{"time":251000,"text":"And I don't mean he made Lego that looked like a slot machine;"},{"time":254000,"text":"I mean he made a slot machine out of Lego."},{"time":256000,"text":"The insides were Lego."}]},{"cues":[{"time":258000,"text":"There's people getting drunk building Lego,"},{"time":260000,"text":"and you've got to finish the thing before you puke."},{"time":263000,"text":"There's a whole gray market for Lego,"},{"time":265000,"text":"thousands of home-based businesses."},{"time":267000,"text":"And some people will fund their entire Lego habit"},{"time":269000,"text":"by selling the little guy,"},{"time":271000,"text":"but then you have no guys in your ships."}]},{"cues":[{"time":273000,"text":"And then, just some examples. This stuff really is sculpture."},{"time":276000,"text":"This is amazing what you can do."},{"time":278000,"text":"And don't kid yourself:"},{"time":280000,"text":"some architectural details, incredible organic shapes"},{"time":283000,"text":"and just, even, nature out of, again, little blocks."},{"time":286000,"text":"This is my house."},{"time":288000,"text":"And this is my house."},{"time":290000,"text":"I was afraid a car was going to come smash it"},{"time":292000,"text":"as I was taking a picture for you guys."}]},{"cues":[{"time":294000,"text":"Anyway, I'm out of time."},{"time":296000,"text":"But just very quickly --"},{"time":299000,"text":"we'll just see if I can do this quick."},{"time":302000,"text":"Because there aren't enough TED logos around here."},{"time":305000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":312000,"text":"Let's see here."},{"time":317000,"text":"Okay."},{"time":323000,"text":"Ta-da."}]},{"cues":[{"time":325000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}